    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK900">
<l>iṟantamainta cārpuṭaiya rāyiṉu muyyār </l>
<l>ciṟantamainta cīrār ceṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though in possession of numerous auxiliaries, they will perish who are-exposed to the wrath of the noble whose penance is boundless.</l>
